me></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-16T17:24:47-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-16T17:24:47-05:00</updated><title> FTC 表示垃圾电话投诉自 2021 年以来大幅下降</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;美元钞票上鹰的图形插图，其形状为智能手机而不是盾牌。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/KybIdzukIeZk8HKTSi0sgVNSoY=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73727876/STK481_STK432_CONGRESS_GOVERNMENT_CIVRGINIA_A.0.jpg&quot; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge； Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;SJYDf3&quot;>;关于骚扰电话的投诉连续第三年下降，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ftc.gov/news-events /news/press-releases/2024/11/reports-unwanted-telemarketing-calls-down-more-50-percent-2021&quot;>;联邦贸易委员会昨天宣布&lt;/a>;。根据 FTC 的数据，此类电话的举报数量与 2021 年相比下降了 50% 以上，这一下降在很大程度上要归功于政府加大力度打击令人恼火的电话营销和电话诈骗。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id= “cdfMA1&quot;>;FTC 写道，2024 财年的骚扰电话投诉比上一年减少了约 33,000 起。尽管该机构写道，有关债务减免电话的报告“比去年增加了 85% 以上”，但这种下降影响了各种不需要的电话。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;2vEKtF&quot;>;FTC 消费者保护局局长 Sam莱文表示，虽然非法电话仍然是“...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/16/24298278/ftc-illegal-scam-call-robocall-telemarketer-complaints-down-50-percent-since-2021&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt; /a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/16/24298278/ftc-illegal-scam-call-robocall-telemarketer-complaints-down-50-percent-since-2021" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/16/24298278/ftc-illegal-scam-call-robocall-telemarketer-complaints-down-50-percent-since-2021</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-16T15:38:47-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-16T15:38:47-05:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的健身追踪器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple Watch、Garmin Epix、Fitbit 和 Amazfit Bip 健身追踪器采用风格化的蓝色背景。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9NfU5CzAkm1H45234kKpT8gicKk=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x8 73/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/70657030/acastro_2203